  "title": "[ AD HOC BASIS ] Locum Staff Nurse (Operating Theatre – Day Surgery / Day Ward ) $29/hr #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Locum Staff Nurse (Operating Theatre – Day Surgery)</strong></p><p><strong>Sector:</strong> Healthcare<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Locum (Ad Hoc Basis)<br /><strong>Location:</strong> West<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $29 per hour</p><p>This role supports day surgery operating theatre services. You will be deployed on an ad-hoc basis when manpower is required. The setting is strictly office hours with no overnight or inpatient cases.</p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Monday to Friday</li><li>8:00am – 5:30pm</li><li>Office hours only</li><li>No night shifts</li></ul></p><p><strong>Work Setting:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Day Surgery Operating Theatre</li><li>No inpatient wards</li><li>No overnight cases</li></ul></p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Assist doctors during day surgery procedures</li><li>Perform scrub and circulating duties</li><li>Prepare and check operating theatre instruments and equipment</li><li>Maintain sterility and safety standards in the operating theatre</li><li>Assist with post-procedure patient monitoring</li><li>Support documentation and daily OT workflow</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Must have prior Operating Theatre / Day Surgery experience</li><li>Able to commit on an ad-hoc locum basis</li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please click “ APPLY NOW”<br /></p><p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p><p>Whatsapp: <a href=\"https://wa.me/+6597430026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://wa.me/+6597430026</a>  </p><p>Email : <a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><br /></p><p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p></p>",
